<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Help Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/common.css" media="screen" title="no title" charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/manual.css" media="screen" title="no title" charset="utf-8">
</head>

<body>
<div class="header">
  <% include ./partials/header %>
</div>
<div class="text">
    <p>
    <ul>
        <div class="title">
            Architecture:
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <div class="headings">Board Structure:</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        5 by 5 board
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        4 sides
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        25 tiles including one home at the center of the board
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Board has 2 loops - outer loop and inner loop
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        4 safe places in the outer loop at a distance of 3 tiles
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Each side has one safe place of outer loop
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
                <div class="headings">Players:</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        4 players
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="headings"> Coins:</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Each player has 4 coins of same colour
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Each player is differentiated by colours
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="headings"> Dice:</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Has 6 sides with number from 1 to 6
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <br/>
        <div class="title">
            Constraints:
        </div>
        <ul class="b">
            <li>
                Each side of the board is the entry point of each player
            </li>
            <li>
                Each player has 4 coins to play with. His/Her target is to take all the four coins from the starting
                position outside the board to the main home.
            </li>
            <li>
                The coin can enter only through safe place.
            </li>
            <li>
                The player has to get 6 on dice while dicing to enter each coin.
            </li>
            <li>
                If the player gets 6 on dice while dicing he/she will get extra chance.
            </li>
            <li>
                While dicing what the player gets on dice the player will move coin according to that number
            </li>
            <li>
                After making a throw, if a player has valid moves, he/she will make the moves, if not, the next player
                gets his/her chance to make the throw in an anti clockwise order.
            </li>
            <li>
                After finishing of valid move of current player next player gets chance.
            </li>
            <li>
                The player want to round the outer loop atleast one time.
            </li>
            <li>
                If the move has resulted in killing a coin (replace a coin) of opponents, current player gets an extra
                chance.
                <br> He/she is also given permission to enter inner loop . Otherwise he/she can not enter into inner
                loop but he/she can possible to round on outer loop repeatedly.
            </li>
            <li>
                The player can not kill the opponent's coin that are in any of the safe places.
            </li>
            <li>
                Multiple pieces of the same player or opponents can be placed together in a safe place.
            </li>
            <li>
                The killed coin has to get out from board.This coin can enter to the game by getting 6 on dice and
                should repeat the same path.
            </li>
            <li>
                The coin has to round inner loop to get into the home.
            </li>
            <li>
                When all coins of a player gets into the main home he/she will win the game. Then the game finished.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </ul>
    </p>
</div>
<div class="footer">
  <% include ./partials/footer  %>
</div>
</body>

</html>
